      <body>
         <div type="writingSession" n="1"><opener><dateline rend="right"><pb facs="Hs-30885,67_001"/><date>10/6 98</date></dateline></opener><p><salute>Lieber Hugo,</salute> die Radpartie war<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ehr<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>chön;<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>eit <date>Din<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>tag</date>
               bin ich in <rs ref="#pmb34860" type="place"><hi rend="latintype">Steindorf</hi></rs>, wo es viel regnet; <date>So<c rendition="#gemination-n">nn</c>tag</date> möcht ich
               gerne in <rs ref="#pmb50" type="place">Wien</rs> eine Nachricht von Ihnen finden, ob
               man Sie vielleicht abends<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ehen kann.</p><closer>Herzlichen Gruß Ihr <signed>Arthur</signed><lb/><signed><handShift scribe="#pmb10863"/>Richard</signed></closer></div>
      </body>
